        Used when a person rents the services of a Grand Master.

        Parameters:
        theId - The id of the GrandMasterTransaction
        theBuyer - the buyer in the GrandMasterTransaction
        theSeller - the seller in the GrandMasterTransaction may be the Grand Master of their agency.
        theAmount - the amount of the GrandMasterTransaction
        theTimestamp - the timestamp of the GrandMasterTransaction
        theSpecialty - the specialty of the Grand Master
        theGrandMasterName - the name of the Grand Master
        theServedTime - the amount of time (minutes) worked by the Grand Master in the transaction
